descriptionHtml:
Immersive Organic Eco Logistic Solutions
AKA The Fishy Stick

Do you feel slightly inadequate when adventuring around Skyrim when you meet new people because you lack the appropriate greeting gift? Well worry no more, nothing breaks the ice better than a lovely Fishy Stick when making new friends.

Now the universal tool of welcome is available for you to create at any cooking station and just watch your dude status increase.

Requirements: Skyrim 1.9, and a stomach for greasy foods.

Know Issues: The name of the mod

Future plans: None I think I've done enough damage to my credibility here already.

Credits:
The author takes no responsibility for the stupid nature of this mod.
author: Mindboggles
